<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.8.2">
<l>malaṅku vilaṅku neṭuveḷḷam maṟuka vaṅkōr varainaṭ</l>
<l>ṭilaṅku cōti yāramuta meytu maḷavō rāmaiyāy</l>
<l>vilaṅkal tiriyat taṭaṅkaṭaluḷ cumantu kiṭanta vittakaṉai,</l>
<l>kalaṅkal munnīrk kaṇṇapurat taṭiyēṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The wise one, who rested as a turtle in the vast sea</l>
<l>Having fixed a mountain there, bearing the mountain while it turned,</l>
<l>So that the crashing, flashing vast flood whirled</l>
<l rend="indent">until glittering, light-filled ambrosia appeared,</l>
<l>I, his servant, saw for myself in Kaṇṇapuram</l>
<l rend="indent">on the murky three waters [of the ocean].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
